                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>15<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> Augt/56</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Rev. Dr. Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">The man whom <persName>Mr. Rubenstein</persName> engaged<lb/> to\n                deliver the Occident, has brought me Six Dollars received<lb/> from\n                    <persName>Messrs. A &amp; L. Mack</persName>, <placeName>Nassau</placeName>\n                <add>?</add> from which he decided<lb/> 30Â¢ for collecting, leaving $5.70 for which\n                please find<lb/> order on <persName>Miss. Moss &amp; Br.</persName> at foot. as I\n                know no other way<lb/> of sending you the money.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The man left with me 4 Nos. of the Occident, 2 directed<lb/> to\n                    <persName>Miss Cohen</persName> at <persName>Mr. N. Phillips</persName>, and\n                    <persName>Mr. Nathl Hart</persName> which<lb/> he could not deliver &amp; 2\n                without any direction to them.<lb/> Please let me know what is to be done with\n                them<lb/> Trusting you are quite well &amp; with kind regards from my<lb/> family I\n                am Rev. dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours very truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Mr Raphall</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>. <placeName>Pha</placeName></p>\n            <p>N.B. The <persName>Miss Cohen</persName> is not the Lady in <placeName>Grand\n                    St.</placeName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30z71h0f/canvas/p1"
